ZH: 我们的新房子有一个宽敞的玄关。
EN: Our new house has a spacious foyer.

ZH: 客厅和玄关之间有一扇门。
EN: There is a door between the living room and the foyer.

ZH: 玄关的地板上铺着漂亮的地毯。
EN: There is a beautiful carpet on the floor of the foyer.

ZH: 玄关里有一个小茶几和一把椅子。
EN: There is a small coffee table and a chair in the foyer.

ZH: 我每天进门后都会把鞋放在玄关。
EN: I always put my shoes in the foyer after I come home every day.

ZH: 这个玄关的设计非常简洁，却很有特色。
EN: The design of this foyer is very simple yet distinct.

ZH: 玄关的墙壁上挂着一幅大画。
EN: There is a large painting hanging on the wall of the foyer.

ZH: 在玄关里有一个可以挂衣服的钩子。
EN: There is a hook in the foyer where you can hang your coat.

ZH: 玄关的天花板上有一个华丽的吊灯。
EN: There is a magnificent chandelier hanging from the ceiling of the foyer.

ZH: 玄关的门前放着一盆绿色的植物。
EN: There is a green plant placed in front of the foyer door.

ZH: 我喜欢坐在玄关的椅子上休息。
EN: I like to sit on the chair in the foyer to relax.

ZH: 玄关里的镜子可以让我整理好头发和衣服。
EN: The mirror in the foyer helps me fix my hair and clothes.

ZH: 玄关通向一个双层楼梯。
EN: The foyer leads to a double-level staircase.

ZH: 玄关的地板是用大理石铺成的。
EN: The floor of the foyer is made of marble.

ZH: 玄关的墙上挂着一幅黑白摄影作品。
EN: There is a black and white photograph hanging on the wall of the foyer.

ZH: 玄关放置了一个鞋柜，方便存放鞋子。
EN: There is a shoe cabinet in the foyer, making it convenient to store shoes.

ZH: 玄关有一个镜子，可以让你检查外观。
EN: There is a mirror in the foyer that allows you to check your appearance.

ZH: 我喜欢玄关上的一个小吊钟。
EN: I like the small clock on the foyer.

ZH: 玄关的装饰灯光给整个房子带来温暖的氛围。
EN: The decorative lighting in the foyer brings a warm atmosphere to the entire house.

ZH: 每次进出房子时，我们都会经过玄关。
EN: Every time we enter or leave the house, we pass through the foyer.
